Builder Design Pattern (Creational Design Pattern)
----------------------

* used to create complex object step by step
* allow different representation of the different object type using same construction code.
* when you want to isolate the construction code from the rest of the codebase or clients.
    to improve the modularity and maintainability.
    
Use cases
   * Application create document like html
   * GUI Creation
   * Meal Ordering
   * Car Manufacturing : Different coolor and Engine Size
   * Web creation  : create different layout and pages
   * Game level design 
   * Database query.


